==<span style="position: relative; display: inline-block; margin-right: 2.5px; top: -2px;">[[File:Untitled205 20240925204431.png|30px|link=]]</span> Entrances and Exits==
===Entrances===
*A vintage train carriage can be found on any outdoor level of the Backrooms. Entering it will bring one to '''Level 61'''.
*Entering a store labeled "Italian Books and Stories" within [[Level 59]].
*Entering a stationary train within the expanse of [[Level 913]] will bring one to '''Level 61'''.
*If a train station is present outside any of [[Level 238|Level 238's]] windows, entering it will lead to '''Level 61'''.
===Exits===
*Noclipping into a table within '''Level 61's''' restaurant car will bring one to [[Level 68]].
*Sometimes a structure will be present within '''Level 61's''' stations, leading to specific levels depending on the structure:
**A house will lead to [[Level 62]].
**A grocery store will lead to [[Level 711]].
**A hotel will lead to [[Level 187]].
**A shopping mall will lead to [[Level 121]].
*Finding a piece of paper labeled "Cowboys, YEEHAW!" will lead to [[Level 695]].
*Noclipping into an out of place vending machine within '''Level 61's''' restaurant car will lead one to [[Level 610]].
